[COLOR red][B]Version 2.1.94[/B][/COLOR]
[B]Needed:[/B]
- No more "Resume from 2%?" popups when starting a new show.
- Only episodes with real progress above 3% will show the resume option.
- Next episode suggestions no longer create false resume points.
- Dialog for resuming playback now ignores tiny progress values.
- Our up-next feature still works, just without the annoying interruption.

